# apollo-graphQL-API

This application runs on ApolloServer and a GraphQL API

HOW TO USE
1. Clone this repository to your local machine
2. CD into the root directory of the cloned files and run "npm init" to install dependencies
3. CD into the src folder and run "node index" to start your server
4. Visit https://localhost:4000 on your browser to send your queries on the GraphQL playground
